This paper deals with the deployment of mobile sensors in wireless sensor networks, which is a topic related to networked systems (cs.NI) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the optimization of sensing quality and energy consumption, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT) and control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper proposes algorithms for optimization, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.MA).
